    "heading": "QuickBooks help, delivered by ProAdvisors.",
    "subheading": "The full spectrum of operational QuickBooks help &mdash; setup, cleanup, migration, payroll configuration, error resolution, file repair, multi-state tax setup, ongoing bookkeeping. Same-day diagnostic for emergencies. Written fixed-fee scope within 3 business days. Delivered by Certified Intuit ProAdvisors. Independent firm.",
    "actions": [
