---

<section class="sec reveal" id="help-disclosure" style="padding-top:32px;padding-bottom:0;">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="disclosure">
      <strong>TechBrot is an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not QuickBooks&rsquo; official support.</strong> For Intuit software-level issues (login, billing, subscription, software bugs), Intuit&rsquo;s own support is the right path. We provide independent, operational help with the accounting work <em>inside</em> QuickBooks. QuickBooks and Intuit are registered trademarks of Intuit Inc.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{#- §01 IN-BRIEF + definition prose render via the in-brief partial slot (speakable #help-in-brief-text + the "What QuickBooks help means" H2). -#}
{%- set definition = [
  "TechBrot is an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm that delivers <strong>operational</strong> QuickBooks help to U.S. small and mid-sized businesses. Operational is the key word: we handle the work that lives inside QuickBooks &mdash; <a href=\"/quickbooks/setup/?intent=quickbooks-setup\">file setup</a>, <a href=\"/quickbooks/cleanup/?intent=qb-cleanup\">structural cleanup</a>, <a href=\"/quickbooks/migration/?intent=quickbooks-migration\">Desktop migration</a>, <a href=\"/accounting/payroll-management/?intent=payroll\">payroll configuration</a>, multi-state tax setup, error resolution, file repair, and ongoing <a href=\"/accounting/bookkeeping/monthly-bookkeeping/?intent=monthly\">monthly bookkeeping</a>.",
  "We do not provide Intuit&rsquo;s own software-level support (login issues, billing, software bugs) &mdash; for those, Intuit&rsquo;s official support is the right path. Every engagement is fixed-fee with a written scope. Same-day diagnostic for emergencies (file corruption, payroll-day failures, year-end deadlines); written scope within 3 business days for scoping conversations. Certified ProAdvisors across all four core platforms &mdash; QBO Level&nbsp;2, Desktop, Enterprise, Payroll &mdash; verifiable on Intuit&rsquo;s public ProAdvisor directory."
] %}
{% include "partials/in-brief.njk" %}

<section class="sec reveal" id="help-triage">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">The diagnostic triage model</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">What kind of QuickBooks help do you actually need?</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">Find your situation &mdash; each routes to the right engagement, with an honest scope and a typical fee.</p>
    <div class="r-2">
      {%- for t in triage %}
      <a class="dc-card hub-card" href="{{ t.href }}"><h3>{{ t.opener | safe }}</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">{{ t.body | safe }}</p><span class="hub-card__go">{{ t.cta | safe }} <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12h15M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span></a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal hub-rt--alt" id="help-urgency" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">By urgency</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:24px;">How fast can we help?</h2>
    <div class="r-3">
      {%- for u in urgency %}
      <div class="dc-card">
        <h3>{{ u.name | safe }}</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">{{ u.who | safe }}</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:8px 0 0;"><strong>Best path:</strong> {% if u.tel %}<a href="tel:{{ site.phone.e164 }}" data-tb-event="phone_click">{{ u.path | safe }}</a>{% else %}{{ u.path | safe }}{% endif %}</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:8px 0 0;"><em>Honest scope:</em> {{ u.scope | safe }}</p>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal" id="help-problems">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Common issues</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:28px;">The QuickBooks problems most U.S. businesses run into.</h2>
    <div class="r-2">
      {%- for p in problems %}
      <div class="dc-card"><h3>{{ p.name | safe }}</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">{{ p.body | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal hub-rt--alt" id="help-operational" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">What it actually looks like</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">What QuickBooks help delivers operationally.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Most &ldquo;QuickBooks help&rdquo; offerings are either too narrow (a one-hour consulting call) or too vague (an ongoing &ldquo;support package&rdquo; with no defined deliverables). TechBrot&rsquo;s engagements are scoped as specific operational projects with specific written deliverables &mdash; a cleanup delivers a reconciled, CPA-ready file with a written summary of what was fixed; a setup delivers a configured file ready to operate from day one; a migration delivers a successfully migrated file with reconciled historical data and rebuilt integrations.</p>
      <p>The work is delivered <strong>inside your QuickBooks file</strong> &mdash; we access as accountant-users, you keep your data, and the audit trail is visible to you at any time. We never operate in a parallel system or require a data export. For recurring engagements, the deliverable is the same shape every month: reconciliation, categorization, financial statements, named-ProAdvisor ownership, and a CPA-ready year-end handoff.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal" id="help-services">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Routed properly</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:28px;">All QuickBooks help, routed properly.</h2>
    <div class="r-3">
      {%- for s in services %}
      <a class="dc-card hub-card" href="{{ s.href }}">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">{{ s.num | safe }}</span>
        <h3>{{ s.name | safe }}</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;color:var(--color-ink-mute);">{{ s.body | safe }}</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14px;margin:10px 0 0;"><strong>{{ s.fee | safe }}</strong> &middot; {{ s.eng | safe }}</p>
        <span class="hub-card__go">{{ s.name | safe }} <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12h15M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal hub-rt--alt" id="help-operator" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Who delivers the help</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Certified ProAdvisors. Every engagement. Every time.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Every TechBrot QuickBooks engagement is delivered by a Certified Intuit QuickBooks ProAdvisor &mdash; not a general bookkeeper, not an offshore queue, not a junior associate. The ProAdvisor team holds active Intuit certifications across all four core platforms: QuickBooks Online (Level 2), Desktop, Enterprise, and Payroll. Renewed annually, verifiable on Intuit&rsquo;s public ProAdvisor directory. The certification is the operational signal &mdash; technical proficiency on the platform you&rsquo;ll be billed for work inside, and third-party accountability to a credentialing body.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-row" style="margin-top:22px;">
      {%- for r in reviewSpec %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value">{{ r.value | safe }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ r.label | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal" id="help-costs">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Pricing</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">What QuickBooks help typically costs.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">All engagements: fixed fee, written scope, no hourly billing. The discovery call is free and no-obligation; specific quotes follow the diagnostic within 3 business days.</p>
    <div class="r-3">
      {%- for c in costs %}
      <div class="dc-card">
        <h3>{{ c.name | safe }}</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;"><strong>For:</strong> {{ c.forWhom | safe }}</p>
        <ul class="checklist" style="margin-top:12px;">
          {%- for b in c.bullets %}<li>{{ b | safe }}</li>{%- endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal hub-rt--alt" id="help-review" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Reviewed by Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisors.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>This page is maintained by the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team at TechBrot Inc., an independent ProAdvisor firm, and reviewed for accuracy on the boundary between operational ProAdvisor help and Intuit&rsquo;s own software support. Where our scope or fees change, this page is updated.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="in-brief__source" style="margin-top:14px;">Page last reviewed: May 2026.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec reveal" id="help-related">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Where else to go</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Where else to go.</h2>
    {%- for n in related %}
    <div style="margin-bottom:18px;">
      <h3><a href="{{ n.href }}">{{ n.title | safe }}</a></h3>
      <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">{{ n.body | safe }}</p>
    </div>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
